<figcaption>This piece is an abstract mirrored art which was made using processing development environment. We have tried to imitate idle scribbling with human-like brushstrokes. Every iteration of the code generates unique artwork. By simply changing certain parameters we can change the essence of the artwork. In the github repository you will find 2 codes: In the first one the brushstrokes are guided by a particle controlled by a physics engine. This stays true to the Code Meets Art ethos of generating an art piece exclusively by code. However to encourage audience interaction we have also added another piece of code wherein the brushstrokes are guided by the mouse pointer.</figcaption>
