<section id="rules" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="rules"><strong>Rules</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>Team Size up to 2 members</li>
<li>Can use any programming language</li>
<li>You are <u><em>not allowed to use machine learning based generations</em></u>. Instead look at the provided samples for inspiration.</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="submission-information" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="submission-information"><strong>Submission Information</strong></h2>
<ul>
